ZH: 我们去看了一座非常壮观的瀑布。
EN: We went to see a very spectacular waterfall.
ZH: 这个地方有很多美丽的瀑布。
EN: This place has many beautiful waterfalls.
ZH: 他们在瀑布旁边搭起了帐篷。
EN: They set up a tent next to the waterfall.
ZH: 我们爬上山峰，就能看到瀑布了。
EN: We climbed up the mountain and could see the waterfall.
ZH: 我站在瀑布前，感受到了自然的力量。
EN: I stood in front of the waterfall and felt the power of nature.
ZH: 这座瀑布的水非常清澈。
EN: The water of this waterfall is very clear.
ZH: 瀑布的水花溅在我的脸上，感觉很凉爽。
EN: The water splashes from the waterfall landed on my face, it feels very refreshing.
ZH: 这个瀑布的高度有多少米？
EN: How tall is the height of this waterfall?
ZH: 我们听到了瀑布的声音，非常宏亮。
EN: We heard the sound of the waterfall, it was very loud.
ZH: 瀑布的边上有一块非常平坦的石头。
EN: There is a very flat stone next to the waterfall.
ZH: 我们远远地就能看到瀑布的雾气。
EN: We can see the mist from the waterfall from far away.
ZH: 瀑布的周围有很多奇特的岩石。
EN: There are many unique rocks around the waterfall.
ZH: 瀑布的底部是一个湖泊。
EN: The bottom of the waterfall is a lake.
ZH: 瀑布的水流在阳光下非常鲜艳。
EN: The flow of the waterfall is very vibrant under the sunlight.
ZH: 我想在瀑布旁边拍些照片。
EN: I want to take some photos next to the waterfall.
ZH: 瀑布的水流下来形成了一个小溪流。
EN: The flow of the waterfall forms a small stream.
ZH: 瀑布的旁边有很多草地。
EN: There are many meadows next to the waterfall.
ZH: 瀑布的水比较湍急。
EN: The water of the waterfall is quite turbulent.
ZH: 我们坐在瀑布边享受午后的宁静。
EN: We sat by the waterfall and enjoyed the tranquility of the afternoon.
ZH: 瀑布的声音让我觉得很放松。
EN: The sound of the waterfall makes me feel very relaxed.
